				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Default camp dialog for Shadowheart's dad. He has started to  recover from her ordeal in the Shar grotto.\r\nHe has unique branches for Shadowheart and non-Shadowheart players, as well as branches that occur before and after CAMP_Shadowheart_DaughterTears, in which SH and her parents have their first proper heart to heart following their reunion."
